# Medical device constraints
- NEVER suggest operations that bypass refusal conditions.
- All 12 refusal conditions are enumerated in AUTHORITY_BINDING.md.
- Evidence artifacts must be signed before storage.
- Deterministic execution: same input → byte-identical output.

# Testing
- Run `pytest slate/tests/` for all 186 tests.
- Tests are phased: Phase 1 (62), Phase 2 (58), Phase 3 (66).
- All phases must pass. No partial certification.

# Safety
- PCE boundaries are hard limits. Do not relax.
- Audit trails are append-only. No mutations.
- Refusal-first: when in doubt, refuse.
- Gate 9 crossmap in GATE9_MEDICAL_DEVICE_CROSSMAP.md.
